, and cook according to packet instructions.","‘Al forno’ is the term given to a dish that has been baked in an oven, which traditionally was wood fired or open flamed. This modern day oven baked pasta dish is perfect for an informal meal with friends as it can be made ahead and then baked when needed. In addition, with this recipe you make your own pasta, an easy task in the Thermomix as all the mixing and kneading is done for you, making an even more impressive meal to serve."],"basicInfo":["medium","40m","1h 55m","4 portions"]}